-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"447\" height=\"144\" src=\"https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-empty-todo-list.png\" alt=\"django formview - empty todo list\" class=\"wp-image-6050\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-empty-todo-list.png 447w, https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-empty-todo-list-300x97.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 447px) 100vw, 447px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you create a new task, you&#8217;ll see only that task in the todo list:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"500\" height=\"505\" src=\"https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-create-task.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6051\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-create-task.png 500w, https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-create-task-297x300.png 297w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"587\" height=\"121\" src=\"https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-own-todo-list.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6052\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-own-todo-list.png 587w, https:\/\/www.pythontutorial.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/django-formview-own-todo-list-300x62.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you attempt to access John&#8217;s tasks while logging in as Jane, you&#8217;ll get a 404 error like this:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"665\" height=\"312\" src=\"https:\/\/www.pythontutori